show.description: Annie, an ordinary girl, crosses paths with Leon, a werewolf leader, bound by a prophecy from the Moon Goddess. Mistaking her sister for his fated mate, Leon falls for Annie as boss and subordinate. When Annie’s memories and powers awaken, their love is tested by secrets, fate, and the truth of her true identity.
